            },
            {
               "text": "### Prerequisites\n\nThis text will delve deeper into the multiplication concepts explored in Chapter 4 of the first volume of the *First Steps* section (<htcite0>) e no texto anterior (<htcite1>).",
               "source": [
                  {
                     "type": 1,
                     "uuid": "b5efc8f9-c268-430f-9681-7a43848ee48e",
                     "text": "History Tracers Team",
                     "page": "First Steps",
                     "date_time": {
                        "type": "gregory",
                        "year": "2024",
                        "month": "",
                        "day": ""
                     }
                  },
                  {
                     "type": 1,
                     "uuid": "c0735d61-b0d7-434c-aec1-ccd6c8589e5c",
                     "text": "History Tracers Team",
                     "page": "Modulating (Part II)",
                     "date_time": {
                        "type": "gregory",
